101
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:21,480
Isa ka lamang bagong silang na Kaluluwa.

102
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,790
Tingnan mo ang kawawa mong kalagayan.

103
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,080
Ikaw dapat
ang pinakamalakas na Demonyo ng Digmaan,

104
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,600
