112
00:13:43,210 --> 00:13:44,440
Wala ka kundi basura.

113
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:45,360
Wala ka nang iba kundi basura!

114
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,820
Wala ka nang iba kundi basura!

115
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,000
Ikaw...

116
00:15:21,090 --> 00:15:23,090
