162
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:33,790
Kaya,

163
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:36,350
Dapat nating gamitin ang prutas na Wugen sa halip.

164
00:17:36,350 --> 00:17:37,640
Gilingin ito hanggang maging pulbos
at tunawin sa tubig.

165
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:39,840
Dapat mainit ang tubig ngunit hindi kumukulo.

166
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:44,000
Hindi kita inaasahan

167
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:46,720
upang maging isang eksperto sa parmakolohiya.

168
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,750
Salamat sa pagliligtas mo sa amin.

169
00:17:51,310 --> 00:17:52,240
Walang anuman.

170
00:17:52,920 --> 00:17:54,030
Xia Xuanzi

171
00:17:54,270 --> 00:17:56,030
