Oo.

183
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:51,520
Pero noong napadaan ako ngayon lang,

184
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,880
Marami akong nakitang mga manggagawa.

185
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:55,920
Dapat mong malaman na

186
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:58,000
Ang Hilagang Xiang ay sikat sa papel.

187
00:18:58,790 --> 00:18:59,310
Oo.

188
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,160
Ang aming gilingan ng papel

189
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:02,540
ay may kasaysayan ng

190
00:19:02,790 --> 00:19:04,510
mahigit 200 taon.

191
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:06,550
Ang papel na aming ginagawa ay

192
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:08,720
manipis at pantay,

193
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,640
puti na parang pinong jade,

194
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:12,240
malambot at siksik,

195
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:14,400
hindi tinatablan ng insekto at init.

196
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:15,640
Ito ay sumisipsip at mabilis matuyo.

197
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:17,570
Ang tinta ay nananatiling matingkad sa ibabaw nito

198
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:19,150
