199
00:19:19,440 --> 00:19:22,200
Napakabenta nito sa merkado.

200
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,550
Paggawa ng papel?

201
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:28,730
Hindi ba ito ang Sekta ng Qinghong?

202
00:19:30,030 --> 00:19:32,360
Kailangan ding kumain at uminom ng Qinghong Sect.

203
00:19:32,830 --> 00:19:34,070
Nang walang industriya

204
00:19:34,350 --> 00:19:35,160
