220
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:14,440
Ilang Hari ng Dharma

221
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,000
at mga Sangay na Guro ng aming sekta

222
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,510
mariing tumutol sa aking

223
00:20:18,270 --> 00:20:20,960
